"{\"uid\": \"cbc.ca-news-canada-british-columbia-olympic-village-school-1.7101026\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Families who took to heart a 2020 promise to fast track a new school in Vancouver's Olympic Village neighbourhood are wondering when - or even if - construction will ever begin.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 72, \"end\": 81, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.903936946622252e-22, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The questions are front of mind for single mom Ashlie Corcoran, who lives and works in Olympic Village, with her son only two years away from entering kindergarten.\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\", \"score\": 0.9972320477722447, \"rank\": 0.0027682071882302404, \"text\": \"Corcoran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\"}, {\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We walk past the plot of land [reserved for the school] every day.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am so hopeful that it is still going to happen,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If it is not, I am going to have to really start thinking about what our next steps are.\\\"\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials have said it will take at least two years to build a school once ground is broken.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So far, the site earmarked for a school over 15 years ago\\u00a0remains untouched.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Village was developed to house athletes from around the world during the 2010 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About 10,000 Vancouverites now call it home.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WATCH | Still no school for Olympic Village:  After 14 years, still no school in Vancouver's Olympic Village  Planning documents from 2007 show a future school site on Columbia Street, adjacent to where Hinge Park is today.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 916, \"end\": 931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}, {\"begin\": 969, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.903936946622252e-22, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2014, theVancouver Sunreported that amid a school space crunch in Vancouver, the Olympic Village school was still awaiting funding and a timeline announcement from B.C.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.903936946622252e-22, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4379240763573492e-24, \"text\": \"B.C.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Liberal government of the day.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After years of BC Liberal neglect, we have started re-investing in our schools.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_Liberal_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BC Liberal\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_Liberal_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_Liberal_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have come a long way, but families in Olympic Village and South False Creek still need a new school.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1464, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/False_Creek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"False Creek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/False_Creek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/False_Creek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A re-elected <a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/bcndp?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\\\">@bcndp</a> government will fast track recovery funding to finally get it built.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"<a href=\\\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BCelxn2020?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\\\">#BCelxn2020</a> <a href=\\\"https://t.co/mGmUpjLARe\\\">https://t.co/mGmUpjLARe</a>  During the 2020 provincial election campaign, the B.C.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NDP ran on a promise to fast-track the school.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999996134834711, \"rank\": 3.5133912267842555e-07, \"text\": \"NDP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pledge was repeated by then-premier John Horgan, Vancouver-Fairview MLA George Heyman and NDP newcomer Brenda Bailey, who flipped the Vancouver-False Creek riding where Olympic Village is located away from Liberal incumbent Sam Sullivan.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Horgan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.519886807651307e-50, \"text\": \"John Horgan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Horgan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Horgan\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver-Fairview\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver-Fairview\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver-Fairview\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver-Fairview\"}, {\"begin\": 1986, \"end\": 1989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legislative_Assembly_of_British_Columbia\", \"score\": 0.999004264181984, \"rank\": 0.0009967282961934236, \"text\": \"MLA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legislative_Assembly_of_British_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legislative_Assembly_of_British_Columbia\"}, {\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 2003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Heyman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"George Heyman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Heyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Heyman\"}, {\"begin\": 2008, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999996134834711, \"rank\": 3.5133912267842555e-07, \"text\": \"NDP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 2021, \"end\": 2034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brenda Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}, {\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Sullivan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Sullivan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q30185\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Sullivan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bailey has said she remains committed to the school but was not available for an interview or to answer questions about a timeline or cost.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"score\": 0.9146386447027902, \"rank\": 0.09326133692444089, \"text\": \"Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vancouver School Board (VSB)\\u00a0Chair Victoria Jung was also not available.\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver School Board\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\"}, {\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.903936946622252e-22, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 2332, \"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"score\": 0.8815611620508156, \"rank\": 0.13435001530526072, \"text\": \"Victoria\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\"}, {\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"score\": 0.9999999965821189, \"rank\": 3.4137165598413046e-09, \"text\": \"Jung\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an emailed statement, Bailey said the province has offered its formal support for the VSB to develop a concept plan for the school.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2396, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"score\": 0.9146386447027902, \"rank\": 0.09326133692444089, \"text\": \"Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For too long, instead of building enough schools to keep up, the previous government refused to invest in students, families and the False Creek area.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are taking a different approach,\\\" wrote Bailey.\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"score\": 0.9146386447027902, \"rank\": 0.09326133692444089, \"text\": \"Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The B.C.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4379240763573492e-24, \"text\": \"B.C.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NDP has been in power since 2017.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999996134834711, \"rank\": 3.5133912267842555e-07, \"text\": \"NDP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Democratic_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to an\\u00a0email from Jung, a school in Olympic Village remains a VSB priority.\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"score\": 0.9999999965821189, \"rank\": 3.4137165598413046e-09, \"text\": \"Jung\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\"}, {\"begin\": 2800, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been the top request in the school district's capital plan funding submission annually for the last number of years,\\\" wrote Jung.\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"score\": 0.9999999965821189, \"rank\": 3.4137165598413046e-09, \"text\": \"Jung\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Central Vancouver's densification has sparked an influx of young families, many attracted by the promise\\u00a0of a walkable lifestyle and car-free living.\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Time_Zone\", \"score\": 0.9990348172255682, \"rank\": 0.0009632251650333693, \"text\": \"Central\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Time_Zone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Time_Zone\"}, {\"begin\": 2988, \"end\": 2997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.903936946622252e-22, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for at least the past decade, school spaces in and around the downtown core have not kept up.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elementary schoolsroutinely hold lotteriesfor scarce kindergarten spots.\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlucky children who do not make the cut end up on wait lists, their families forced to travel\\u00a0to\\u00a0schools in other neighbourhoods\\u00a0that do\\u00a0have space.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or families choose to pick up and move elsewhere.\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Olympic Village families, the \\\"kindergarten lotto stress,\\\" as Corcoran calls it, is even more pronounced.\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}, {\"begin\": 3568, \"end\": 3576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\", \"score\": 0.9972320477722447, \"rank\": 0.0027682071882302404, \"text\": \"Corcoran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only without a neighbourhood school, parental anxiety is generated by the lottery at catchment school Simon Fraser Elementary, a 25-minute walk away.\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's not a walkable experience for a kindergartener,\\\" said Corcoran.\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3825, \"end\": 3833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\", \"score\": 0.9972320477722447, \"rank\": 0.0027682071882302404, \"text\": \"Corcoran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wilson_Corcoran\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will have to drive there and become another car in morning traffic.\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we might not even get into that school, and so, if we are sent to a school in East Vancouver, or a school in South Vancouver, then we may need to think about where we live.\\\"\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 4085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3995, \"end\": 4004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.903936946622252e-22, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an email, the Ministry of Education said staff are working quickly to review a report from the VSB about an Olympic Village school.\", \"from\": 4087, \"to\": 4221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4198, \"end\": 4213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"score\": 0.9996704418275155, \"rank\": 0.0003296668168300043, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The province and district appreciate everyone's patience while this process continues,\\\" reads the email.\", \"from\": 4223, \"to\": 4328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The site has been complex and has required some additional planning time.\\\"\", \"from\": 4329, \"to\": 4404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Corcoran remains hopeful the provincial budget will have answers when it's released later this month.\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really hoping that the city, the school board and the province can all get on the same page right now and provide this resource that's so needed,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With a provincial election scheduled for the fall, plans made now by the government could go by the wayside if another party wins power.\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@CBCLarsen  Karin Larsen is a former Olympian and award winning sports broadcaster who covers news and sports for CBC Vancouver.\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 4939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4848, \"end\": 4856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"sco